metadata.name: LABYRINTH
metadata.description:
SOULTREES by Louis Iruela - LABYRINTH  
2022. Madrid.  
6508px x 3332px

SOULTREES is a compilation of photographs that portrays nature from an intimate point of view, with trees and forests as the common theme.  
This body of work has a romantic and surrealist mood, the product of countless rainy morning walks and hours of experimental and creative editing.
